## Alias

render_reference



## Usage

```r
render_reference(rd_file, output_file, config_file = "_starlightr.toml")
```



## Examples

```r
# Not run:
render_reference(
  rd_file = "man/function.Rd",
  output_file = "../Docs/src/content/docs/reference/function.mdx",
  config_file = "_starlightr.toml"
)
```
